{"tid":2077708,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林兆彬: 反對旺角警署餐廳賣酒的最後機會","createTime":"2020-06-24T12:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T13:31:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"160b720ad3537d2588e2179f51f642d2c7015caa","tid":2077708,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E8%B3%A3%E9%85%92%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E9%2585%2592%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPjnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=b6d9f871\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E9%2585%2592%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%259C%2583%2F&h=379e2d5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E8%B3%A3%E9%85%92%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83/</a><br />\n<br />\n你有沒有想像過，旺角警署入面原來有間餐廳賣酒？<br />\n<br />\n今年 6 月 2 日，酒牌局就旺角警署警官餐廳申請續領會社酒牌召開聆訊，我作為當區區議員，帶同 1,676 個反對簽名與街坊一起出席聆訊，發言反對續牌。當日，我才首次從文件中得知餐廳的外貌，因為在互聯網上根本找不到任何資料。最終，酒牌局漠視民意，仍然續發兩年牌照。<br />\n<br />\n我們不用灰心，因為仍有一個最後的反對機會，根據《應課稅品（酒類）規例》17(5) 條，只要集合至少 20 名居住在旺角警署附近 400 米半徑範圍的街坊，就可以向市政服務上訴委員會提出上訴。我暫時仍未收到酒牌局的正式結果通知，而當收到通知之後，根據法例，我須於 28 日內提出上訴。希望大家可以致電 6731-9751 聯絡我，安排填寫上訴表格。"},{"pid":"eaa6b84abb6dfa2b9dee063ca06f50c1dda4bbf0","tid":2077708,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"af3017c431391b77335252ecd987fcf70ca39a63","tid":2077708,"uid":48947,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"反對黎把撚咩<br />\n由得佢地飲鳩醉晒抆槍互射啦"},{"pid":"361f7d561dd9109ccfaf04ae6e263c717cc78a9c","tid":2077708,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9e80ce32ab4432a5f7b0352158d3ecc90e2669c","tid":2077708,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e34b94b7b33925aed22cd8e02948071a5779637c","tid":2077708,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:02:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a04dcc24fceef8dfc8cab0f0b0bb77898ecabf9d","tid":2077708,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:04:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"80d13d3ad73c30f5b620a7947c62f21e4547c71d","tid":2077708,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbc5ffada289a78572d19185dd2e167d3cee5ca","tid":2077708,"uid":35438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b74eddc0c068b263f3517f7b6099de6ae5568a61","tid":2077708,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.